<p>An Indian Air Force Tejas fighter jet crashed during a demonstration at the Dubai Air Show on Friday at Al Maktoum International Airport, killing the pilot, Wing Commander Namansh Syal, 34 [ndtv.com#2]. The Indian Air Force confirmed the fatality and said a court of inquiry is being constituted to ascertain the cause [dawn.com#1]. The crash occurred at about 2:10 pm local time on the show’s final day [dawn.com#1].</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/bbHRKZM7Nv0AiXIELnU0hVhSLv1punOdvSLIBJiPzzWCYm-4_dOOJyxxtErM7kQu3EwuFuVLnNbxVDdxUioeFq5d8B-_NsZ4B6EECxJABh9fd2nBHwgJ1ZmUsYOTf10cXRKG_hgQojJx8yx8Fg-O1qNtLLM5ZGdMlKLD2i5Nk0QyMsKC1sUoSJPNSLVwlGDamf9cOOWReTOLR5Rpv7bUue16cfvLF4XO4T2elyOOrJr83W8nnojzfAk3rA' alt='The Indian HAL Tejas performing moments before the crash during a Dubai Air Show demonstration.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Video and witness accounts indicate the aircraft attempted a low roll and appeared to lose control before diving toward the ground and erupting in flames [dawn.com#1][abc.net.au#1]</li><li>The incident happened about a mile (1.6 km) from the main show site during the afternoon flying display, with hundreds of spectators present [dawn.com#1]</li><li>Official response: The IAF announced a court of inquiry; India’s embassy said it is in touch with UAE authorities; the UAE aviation authority was not immediately available to comment on leading a local investigation [dawn.com#1]</li><li>Program context: In September, India placed a $7 billion order for 97 upgraded Tejas Mk1A jets to replace its MiG-21 fleet [dawn.com#1]</li></ul><blockquote>An IAF Tejas aircraft met with an accident during an aerial display at Dubai Air Show, today. The pilot sustained fatal injuries in the accident. - Indian Air Force (post on X, quoted by Dawn)</blockquote><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Indian Air Force: The IAF confirmed the pilot’s death and said a court of inquiry is being constituted to ascertain the cause [dawn.com#1] (<a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1956499/indias-indigenous-tejas-fighter-aircraft-crashes-at-dubai-air-show'>Dawn</a>)</li><li>Indian Embassy in UAE: The embassy said it is in touch with UAE authorities following the crash [dawn.com#1] (<a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1956499/indias-indigenous-tejas-fighter-aircraft-crashes-at-dubai-air-show'>Dawn</a>)</li><li>UAE aviation authority: Officials were not immediately available to comment on whether they would lead a local investigation [dawn.com#1] (<a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1956499/indias-indigenous-tejas-fighter-aircraft-crashes-at-dubai-air-show'>Dawn</a>)</li><li>Spectators: Hundreds were watching from a grandstand as the jet went down during the display [dawn.com#1] (<a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1956499/indias-indigenous-tejas-fighter-aircraft-crashes-at-dubai-air-show'>Dawn</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1956499/indias-indigenous-tejas-fighter-aircraft-crashes-at-dubai-air-show'>India’s indigenous Tejas fighter aircraft crashes at Dubai Air Show</a> - dawn.com</li><li><a href='https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/tejass-dubai-air-show-crash-namansh-syal-witness-says-no-one-could-believe-it-9681086#publisher=newsstand'>&quot;No One Could Believe It&quot;: Witness To NDTV On Tejas Jet Crash At Dubai Air Show</a> - ndtv.com</li><li><a href='https://www.abc.net.au/news/2025-11-22/pilot-killed-in-indian-fighter-jet-crash/106039602'>Pilot killed in Indian fighter jet crash during demo flight at Dubai Air Show</a> - abc.net.au</li><li><a href='https://apnews.com/article/dubai-air-show-plane-crash-9df3d47f6220c7772a1d24762b0e2836'>An Indian Air Force HAL Tejas crashes at the Dubai Airshow in Dubai, United Arab Emirates, killing the pilot.</a> - apnews.com</li></ul>